om better technology in the same wayHope this keeps the flames away  Have fun Stephan neuhaus@informatikunikldesig closed for inventory  Please leave your pickaxe outsidePGP 22 public key available on request  Note the expiration date" confidence="0.2" support="20" types="" sparql="" policy="whitelist">
